+## Review Reply Draft
+
+`T-214-01`
+Addressed in `src/policy/approval_router.py` and `src/policy/preview.py`. The router now normalizes `manual_review` to `human_review_required` before building the preview payload, and the preview-unavailable fallback now preserves both `approval_state` and `requires_human_review`.
+
+`T-214-02`
+No separate change. This is a duplicate of `T-214-01`, and the fallback fix above resolves the same reopened regression.
+
+`T-214-03`
+Not applied. The exported review marks this thread outdated, and the suggested legacy branch revival does not match the current branch state. No legacy preview alias was added.
+
+`T-214-04`
+Addressed in `tests/test_preview.py`. Added a regression test covering `build_policy_preview(..., preview_enabled=False, approval_state="manual_review", ...)` and asserting the fallback keeps `approval_state="human_review_required"` with `requires_human_review=true`.
+
+`T-214-05`
+Addressed in `docs/approval_policy.md`. The fallback example now shows the corrected payload with `approval_state` and `requires_human_review`.
